    base:desc "The framework provides real‑time data exchange that continuously synchronizes the physical building with its digital replica. Updates are propagated as soon as sensor readings or control actions occur, implying a near‑zero latency loop suitable for device‑level monitoring and control. Temporal granularity is at the level of individual building devices (e.g., HVAC units, lighting fixtures). No explicit numerical frequency is specified."
